A serial killer and a hitman.

13
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:53,960
 If anger can't find an exit and overflows,

14
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:57,790
 no one knows which direction it will go.

15
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:04,450
 Anger easily changes direction.

16
00:01:04,450 --> 00:01:08,060
 And it rushes on.

17
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,730

18
00:01:10,730 --> 00:01:13,640
Over there!

19
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:19,920
 After that, it rages like a wave with uncontrollable speed

20
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:23,850
 and swallows the truth.

21
00:01:23,850 --> 00:01:28,180
 Like that, it strikes everything

22
