Criticism and curses spewed recklessly are nothing but excrement.

31
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:05,370
Anger like that can't face justice.

32
00:02:05,370 --> 00:02:10,540
When it comes to the emotion of anger, refined language and attitudes are needed.

33
00:02:10,540 --> 00:02:14,660
Isn't it necessary to understand anger in order to properly soothe it?

34
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:18,960
Yes. To begin with, I think that we may need to soothe this anger first.

35
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:21,830
There are more than a few patients who are saying that they will leave the hospice, too!

36
00:02:21,830 --> 00:02:24,020
H-H-How many?

37
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:27,900
What are you going to do? You've seen the articles about the third murder, haven't you?

38
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:31,660
People are going crazy saying that Min Woo Cheon and Pyo In Sook killed him while on the run.

39
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:33,030
That won't be true.

40
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:36,660
I don't know anymore! I can't be sure that it isn't true.

41
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:40,150
- They are in love. 
 - Pardon?

42
