50
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,560
Nothing has been confirmed yet.

51
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,560
Yet?

52
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:48,660
Keep that in mind. She ran away because you guys are barking up the wrong tree!

53
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:52,720
You couldn't catch the real killer from the beginning,

54
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:55,130
you're torturing that innocent kid,

55
