My In Sook said that she didn't kill them...

57
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:14,910
Isn't catching criminals your job?

58
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:20,490
You shouldn't be sitting here, go catch the real culprit!

59
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:22,380
Grandma!

60
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:25,650
Grandma!

61
00:04:25,650 --> 00:04:27,690
Please get up.

62
00:04:29,980 --> 00:04:32,250
Forget it. I'm fine.

63
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:35,580
Since I'm all right, give me San Ah and go to work.

64
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:36,980
No.

65
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:42,350
Go. Even if the world turns upside down, you need to work in order to eat.

66
00:04:42,350 --> 00:04:44,190
Come with me.

67
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:49,250
Come with me to the hospice. I have to make lunch.

68
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:58,750
Announcing an open search for Min Woo Cheon was going too far.

69
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:02,220
